<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/to-the-oligarchy-democracy-is-just-a-marionette-to-be-manipulated/">To the Oligarchy, Democracy Is Just a Marionette to Be Manipulated</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">We are conducting elections, but not under conditions that allow for a diversity of viewpoints and opposition to be heard.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/derek-d-cressman/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Derek D. Cressman</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://www.bkconnection.com/' itemprop='url'>Berrett-Koehler Publishers</a></span></dd>
</dl>
